title: What to Watch in the Markets this Week
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin, deputy editor Ben Levisohn and Michael Contopoulos, director of fixed income at Richard Bernstein Advisors discuss the outlook for financial markets, industry sectors, and individual stocks.
